api_list.name: Main request point
api_list.description:
Request **URL **to catalog page
 like .../shop/search/Pageindex/1?keyword=michael%20kors&cm_kws_ac=Mich 
Request **UrlPageQuery **page query with param {PageNumber} 
 If Url is like in example, then page query will be: .../shop/search/Pageindex/{PageNumber}?keyword=michael%20kors&cm_kws_ac=Mich

**MaxPageNumber **- How many pages parse
 
**Cookies ** - Can set some cookies, recomended for Culure
     
**ListOfWordsToRemove ** - Words to remove from parsed Name and Description
   
 **LoadImagesAsBase64String  ** If is true then images loaded in Base64 string format
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://macys-scrapper-service.p.rapidapi.com/api/webparser/loadmacys"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "macys-scrapper-service.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.post(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
